creator: Bolesław Prus
description:
LibriVox recording of Lalka (tom 2) by Bolesław Prus. Read in Polish by Piotr Nater. Drugi tom klasycznego dzieła Bolesława Prusa o miłości kupca Stanisława Wokulskiego do młodej arystokratki Izabeli Łęckiej osadzonego w szczegółowo odmalowanej Warszawie - Summary by Piotr Nater For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B 01-15 (150MB) Download M4B 16-28 (145MB)
